    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/06/22/vscode 插件evermonkey 同步印象笔记/</id>
    <published>2018-06-22T08:52:30.243Z</published>
    <updated>2018-06-22T08:52:30.243Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="vscode-插件evermonkey-同步印象笔记"><a href="#vscode-插件evermonkey-同步印象笔记" class="headerlink" title="vscode 插件evermonkey 同步印象笔记"></a>vscode 插件evermonkey 同步印象笔记</h1><p>印象笔记不支持markdown，可以在vscode中编辑然后在用<code>evermoneky</code>插件同步到印象笔记中。</p><p>首先你得有个账号，然后下一步是创建<code>evelop token</code>,现在印象笔记已将创建<code>develop token</code>关闭，因此只能手动申请<a href="https://www.yinxiang.com/contact/support/ticket/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">申请地址</a>。</p><p>申请提交后大概一两天客服会发邮件告诉你已经开通了<code>develop token</code>.</p><p>点击一下链接登录后即可<br><a href="https://app.yinxiang.com/api/DeveloperToken.action" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://app.yinxiang.com/api/DeveloperToken.action</a></p><div align="center"><br><br><img src="http://p8gdfbtx6.bkt.clouddn.com/2018-06-22-16-35-23-2018622.png" alt="2018-06-22-16-35-23-2018622"><br></div><p>vscode安装<code>evermoneky</code>插件，然后　首先项－打开用户配置，找到<code>evermoneky</code>插件的配置信息进行如下编辑<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&quot;evermonkey.noteStoreUrl&quot;: </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;evermonkey.token&quot;: ,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;files.eol&quot;: &quot;\n&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;[markdown]&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;editor.quickSuggestions&quot;: true</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;evermonkey.noteReadonly&quot;: false,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
    
